<p>In the latest development in Switzerland’s New Year’s tragedy, an 18-year-old Swiss national has died in a Zurich hospital from injuries sustained in the Alpine bar fire, raising the confirmed death toll to 41. The blaze broke out in the early hours of January 1 at Le Constellation, a bar in the Crans-Montana ski resort. Authorities say many of those hurt were young people, and a number of the injured remain hospitalized with severe burns. Prosecutors have opened a criminal investigation into the bar’s owners as officials continue to examine what caused the fire.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/z5tobEmMLnT2Ql_kG-4ocZ0UKdxi7jd3cxTOKL1LyOp18V7qhK3DrfdkuU44UYMeffvVNxzRPspkvRLCAQ2R0q95BBQ6SLp8_9ToN-5qOXQ77eMViJ0CXsRak8FCrAbGNbCqspYgcaIpLQQWcunxHlY9QuIIwSVBeqQRwOjcQRJpjpEhC9GJTb-nqcLfiYjD-DxJYbbFIfYZWUcqF8Iv0-XWZnMhIGUf4exdxj4CTMPxnj9MMGp7IKL1lmvoCcMe77ctf7HFJp3-YA8bfA' alt='Flower tributes are placed at the entrance of the Le Constellation bar and lounge in Crans-Montana, Switzerland, after the New Year’s fire.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Possible ignition: Euronews reported investigators’ early view that sparklers likely ignited foam inside the venue, a detail central to determining how quickly the fire spread.</li><li>Injury burden: RFI said the disaster injured 155 people, underlining the scale of long-term medical and recovery needs beyond the fatalities.</li><li>Protest march: Several hundred demonstrators marched in Lausanne seeking “justice and truth” as the investigation unfolds, according to RFI.</li><li>Local prosecutor: The BBC reported the local prosecutor announced the teenager’s death after treatment in Zurich, reflecting the formal judicial oversight of the case.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Swiss prosecutors: Prosecutors have opened a criminal investigation into the owners of Le Constellation bar while examining circumstances surrounding the blaze. (<a href='https://www.npr.org/2026/02/01/nx-s1-5695756/swiss-alpine-bar-fire-claims-41st-victim'>NPR</a>)</li><li>Demonstrators in Lausanne: Marchers called for “justice and truth” about the fire and accountability as authorities investigate. (<a href='https://www.rfi.fr/en/international/20260201-death-toll-from-swiss-bar-fire-rises-to-41-as-protesters-demand-justice'>RFI</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/death-toll-of-swiss-new-year-bar-blaze-rises-to-41'>Death toll of Swiss ski resort blaze rises to 41</a> - straitstimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/2/1/death-toll-from-swiss-new-year-alpine-bar-fire-increases-to-41'>Death toll from Swiss New Year Alpine bar fire increases to 41</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c0lxr1ne52ro'>Teenager dies from Swiss bar fire injuries, bringing death toll to 41</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.ndtv.com/world-news/swiss-bar-fire-claims-another-victim-death-count-rises-to-41-10926608#publisher=newsstand'>Swiss Bar Fire Claims Another Victim, Death Count Rises To 41</a> - ndtv.com</li><li><a href='https://www.rfi.fr/en/international/20260201-death-toll-from-swiss-bar-fire-rises-to-41-as-protesters-demand-justice'>Death toll from Swiss bar fire rises to 41 as protesters demand &#x27;justice&#x27;</a> - rfi.fr</li><li><a href='http://www.euronews.com/2026/02/01/death-toll-from-new-years-eve-fire-in-switzerland-rises-to-41'>Death toll from New Year&#x27;s eve fire in Switzerland rises to 41</a> - euronews.com</li><li><a href='https://www.npr.org/2026/02/01/nx-s1-5695756/swiss-alpine-bar-fire-claims-41st-victim'>Swiss Alpine bar fire claims 41st victim, an 18-year-old Swiss national</a> - npr.org</li><li><a href='https://www.france24.com/en/europe/20260201-death-toll-from-crans-montana-new-year-bar-fire-rises-to-41'>Death toll from Crans-Montana New Year&#x27;s Eve bar fire rises to 41</a> - france24.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theglobeandmail.com/world/article-switzerland-new-year-bar-fire-le-constellation/'>Death toll in Switzerland’s New Year’s bar fire rises to 41</a> - theglobeandmail.com</li></ul>